regions.content: wondered about the location of a hotel
poured the flour onto the counter
bothered him about the trip to the beach
skimmed the reading for the week
the last movement of the performance
the people who were still in the building
lifted the chickens from their coop
piled the seeds in long rows
attacked the house with high-powered hoses
changed a critical part of the story
to see if she was skipping school
the client because of the unpaid bills
every second Tuesday of the month
created a solution to the well-known problem
charged the bars of their cage
when they charged the bars of their cage
remained on the runway for a long time
climbed the big rock that blocked the path
the enemy hide in the jungle
predicted a good year for the industry
with the dent already in it
the way he tutored the younger players
